<plot>Psychological drama between Catarina and Dudu, a mid class couple, who live together in Rio de Janeiro. She is a model, and he is a painter. The relationship seems to be very well, until Catarina travels by herself. Dudu is by himself at home, and has a jealousy crisis, and opens her email. Dudu finds out the truth about her; a Secret, which will change their lives. This is an "actor's film". The director Luis Antonio Pereira gathered for his first film a great team of well-known Brazilian actors and crew.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?405034</url></doc>
